arStrings.szText: My investigations into the Triune cult point towards the fallen city of Guulrahn. I should meet Lorath there as soon as possible.

We enter the blood-soaked streets of Guulrahn. Oyuun, a prisoner who holds secrets necessary to enter the palace, languishes in the depths of the city. We must brave the charnel alleys to reach the prison and rescue Oyuun.
We head to the outskirts of Guulrahn to reunite with Oyuun and find a path into the palace.

The gore-ridden sewers of Guulrahn hold a hidden path into the palace. Using Oyuun's details, we hunt for the secret passage into the palace undercroft. With the palace breached, Magnus is within reach.
